{"tid":2250673,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"本港失業率升至6.4%　16年新高","createTime":"2020-10-20T09:16:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T12:09:51.000Z","uid":20933,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c8dee6385db4afad113b1d2899df8f73aa9a44c7","tid":2250673,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:16:45.000Z","msg":"據政府統計處今日（20日）發表的最新勞動人口統計數字，經季節性調整的失業率由今年6至8月的6.1%，上升至7至9月的6.4%；失業率見近16年新高，對上一次失業率錄得6.4%已是2004年11月至2005年1月。就業不足率在該兩段期間則保持不變，維持於3.8%的水平。<br />\n<br />\n7至9月期間，大多數主要經濟行業的失業率（不經季節性調整）均見上升，其中零售、住宿及膳食服務業，以及藝術、娛樂及康樂活動業有相對明顯的上升。就業不足率方面，下跌主要見於運輸業和教育業，而上升則主要見於餐飲服務活動業和藝術、娛樂及康樂活動業。<br />\n<br />\n總就業人數由6至8月的3,640,400人，下跌至7至9月的3,624,800人，減少約15,600人。同期的總勞動人口亦由3,888,800人下跌至3,884,600人，減少約4200人。"},{"pid":"71f86f2131df1a6e089856c53fba1799e5a08871","tid":2250673,"uid":9633,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:24:20.000Z","msg":"上一輩上撚晒岸話知你20%"},{"pid":"61db78b48716f3a8476a6b4db4c6de6ac1337315","tid":2250673,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:26:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a66433a3252f5aed38a6a6aed3489a2b1fc7ad","tid":2250673,"uid":19196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:36:39.000Z","msg":"最衰國泰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbb77d50879ff0ad8cd73173679f59bbe306630b","tid":2250673,"uid":161374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:37:21.000Z","msg":"然而樓價照升"},{"pid":"0f01446f9d97007d0345dbd29eb34c7d8ddb30f8","tid":2250673,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"76a66433a3252f5aed38a6a6aed3489a2b1fc7ad","tid":2250673,"uid":19196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"